nodes.text: Shobquix Yards produced the Toscan 8-Q starfighter, one of the precursors to Koensayr's Y-wing starfighter. The fighter was so notable that the company was sometimes referred to as the Toscan corporation.
Secrets of the Sisar Run names the makers of the "Tocsan Q-8" as "Tocsan" corporation. The fighter's name was, however, changed in later sources to "Toscan", probably owing to a typo.
